{"tid":1981150,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"前隊友回顧伊巴謙霸氣 「我銀行有3億，仲有個島！」","createTime":"2020-04-20T13:22:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T06:02:08.000Z","uid":67225,"like":81,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"e604c5b46ba46df2887a4de6c4e28da89d0f7d7b","tid":1981150,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:22:09.000Z","msg":"伊巴謙轉戰美職聯後，56場攻入52球，之後返回歐洲效力AC米蘭。現被借到葡超唐迪拉的祖奧柏度回想一次洛杉磯銀河作客侯斯頓戴拿模：「我們領先1：0，然後他們反擊，打成2：2，最後階段他們踢成3：2，後來伊巴謙嚴厲批評我們。他說：『如果你們來是去沙灘，逛荷里活，只管說就可以，但現在告訴我。我銀行有3億，也有一個島，我根本不需要這樣。第一個開口的我會殺了他，我真的會。』」<br />\n<br />\n伊巴謙的霸氣早已不是秘密，他曾在打破銀河球季入球紀錄後說自己是踢過美職聯最佳的球員。祖奧柏度亦提到有次訓練要踢11對11的比賽：「有人問誰要開球。助教說『祖奧柏度吧，今天是他生日。』伊巴謙轉身說：『天天都是我的生日，把球給我。』然後他大笑。」(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=1E6MrqGGcFSEGQF%2FdL0KzYVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=33906677\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.q_sZJcNrEPewuS0uBXY4g--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/ca/goal.com.hk/4c81a86556b3369e234dc61edf5c3370\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F.q_sZJcNrEPewuS0uBXY4g--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fca%2Fgoal.com.hk%2F4c81a86556b3369e234dc61edf5c3370&h=a705e99e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3cf1b0dc9efd9a1e5edf93c1f9f69f0e060ed37a","tid":1981150,"uid":129733,"like":78,"dislike":5,"score":73,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:24:25.000Z","msg":"廢老9upper<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65b5ee937e92eae8826aa202062eed0f828dd383","tid":1981150,"uid":29929,"like":2,"dislike":32,"score":-30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:25:23.000Z","msg":"如果你們來是去沙灘，逛荷里活，只管說就可以，但現在告訴我。我銀行有3億，也有一個島，我根本不需要這樣。第一個開口的我會殺了他，我真的會。<br />\n<br />\n係佢有定隊友有？"},{"pid":"f5925fe6e8800cf01e4f9ac7cdffbbc2f98dd8a0","tid":1981150,"uid":52571,"like":116,"dislike":1,"score":11